<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <title>Farmtech | Alertes critiques</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 24px 0;
            background: #0f172a;
            color: #e5e7eb;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .wrap {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 14px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .card {
            background: #111827;
            border: 1px solid #1f2937;
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .brand {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #7fc89a, #5cae78);
            color: #07210f;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 18px 20px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 22px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            color: #f9fafb;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0 0 14px;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            line-height: 1.45;
        }
        .stats {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-spacing: 10px 0;
            margin: 0 -10px 14px;
        }
        .stat {
            border: 1px solid #273246;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px;
            width: 50%;
            background: #0b1220;
        }
        .stat-label {
            display: block;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .stat-value {
            display: block;
            color: #f9fafb;
            font-size: 25px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #273246;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .table th,
        .table td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #273246;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .table th {
            color: #d1d5db;
            background: #162133;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .table td {
            color: #e5e7eb;
            background: #0b1220;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 3px 9px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }
        .badge-danger {
            color: #fecaca;
            background: #4c1d1d;
            border: 1px solid #7f1d1d;
        }
        .badge-warning {
            color: #fde68a;
            background: #422006;
            border: 1px solid #78350f;
        }
        .section-title {
            margin: 18px 0 8px;
            color: #f3f4f6;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .muted {
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="brand">FARMTECH</div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Alerte stock et maintenance</h1>
            <p>Bonjour, voici le rapport automatique des alertes critiques.</p>

            <table role="presentation" class="stats">
                <tr>
                    <td class="stat">
                        <span class="stat-label">Produits en stock bas (seuil {{ threshold }})</span>
                        <span class="stat-value">{{ low_stock_count }}</span>
                    </td>
                    <td class="stat">
                        <span class="stat-label">Matériels en panne</span>
                        <span class="stat-value">{{ panne_count }}</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <h2 class="section-title">Produits en stock bas</h2>
            {% if low_stock_products is empty %}
                <p>Aucun produit sous le seuil.</p>
            {% else %}
                <table class="table" role="presentation">
                    <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Produit</th>
                        <th>Quantité</th>
                        <th>Unité</th>
                        <th>Statut</th>
                    </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                    {% for produit in low_stock_products %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>{{ produit.nom }}</td>
                            <td>{{ produit.quantite }}</td>
                            <td>{{ produit.unite }}</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-warning">Stock bas</span></td>
                        </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            {% endif %}

            <h2 class="section-title">Matériels en panne</h2>
            {% if broken_materiels is empty %}
                <p>Aucun matériel en panne.</p>
            {% else %}
                <table class="table" role="presentation">
                    <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Matériel</th>
                        <th>Produit lié</th>
                        <th>État</th>
                    </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                    {% for materiel in broken_materiels %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>{{ materiel.nom }}</td>
                            <td>{{ materiel.produit ? materiel.produit.nom : 'N/A' }}</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-danger">Panne</span></td>
                        </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            {% endif %}

            <p class="muted">Cet email a été généré automatiquement par Farmtech (Stock interne).</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
